[This report expands the outbreak to include 5 cases in the Columbus area.
It is as yet unclear whether all of the Ohio cases have a common source.
It is noteworthy that there has been a recall of beef patties issued by a
nationwide distributor from New England because of _E. coli_ contamination,
but there is no indication that these products are related to the Ohio
outbreak as yet. - Mods.ES/MPP
